Name: BlackJack Math Cross Numbers
About the game: Welcome to BlackJack Math Cross Numbers! Tease your brain in this mix of crosswords with blackjack, in this game you need to match all the maths in the colums and lines with 21 as result. Key Features Hand-made levels that will test your math skills. Originally composed music to keep you relaxed while solving the puzzles.
